<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 10:07:41 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国正在缓慢而谨慎地在加沙问题上为以色列划定红线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-slowly-and-carefully-drawing-red-lines-for-israel-on-gaza/0000018b-9414-db71-a7df-fdddf39d0000</link><description>最近一周，白宫关于以色列-加沙战争的信息发生了转变，官员们谈到了加沙的人道主义暂停，总统乔·拜登向以色列施压，要求其控制极端主义的约旦河西岸定居者</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 08:12:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-is-slowly-and-carefully-drawing-red-lines-for-israel-on-gaza/0000018b-9414-db71-a7df-fdddf39d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国国务卿布林肯在以色列会见内塔尼亚胡，以色列国防军又任命了四名在加沙丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-live/blinken-to-push-for-humanitarian-pause-as-israeli-army-encircles-gaza-city/0000018b-9334-db7e-af9b-fbf78ad50000</link><description>23 名以色列士兵和军官在加沙地面攻势中丧生 ■ 布林肯周五降落在以色列，预计将推动以色列在加沙战斗中“人道主义暂停” ■ 官员称，美国在加沙上空飞行无人机搜寻人质 ■ 以色列国防军在黎巴嫩发动空袭导弹发射 ■ 242 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称加沙有 9,000 多人丧生</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-live/blinken-to-push-for-humanitarian-pause-as-israeli-army-encircles-gaza-city/0000018b-9334-db7e-af9b-fbf78ad50000</guid></item><item><title>在东西方之间，内塔尼亚胡现在确实处于自己的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/between-east-and-west-netanyahu-really-now-is-a-league-of-his-own/0000018b-91bc-d477-a1ff-f7bc76240000</link><description>一边是乌克兰和美国，一边是卡塔尔和俄罗斯：已经发生和将要发生的一切都发生在这两个轴心之间 ■ 摩萨德前局长尤西·科恩回归的背后是什么？ ■ 斯莫特里奇努力点燃约旦河西岸，同时永远不会忘记照顾他的基地</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:02:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/between-east-and-west-netanyahu-really-now-is-a-league-of-his-own/0000018b-91bc-d477-a1ff-f7bc76240000</guid></item><item><title>纳斯鲁拉期待已久的讲话可能决定战争的进程和黎巴嫩的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-long-awaited-speech-could-dictate-the-course-of-the-war-and-lebanons-future/0000018b-9185-db71-a7df-fdcd1cda0000</link><description>美国在该地区的强大存在使得真主党和伊朗更有可能保持谨慎 ■ 以色列领导人铲除哈马斯的承诺只是口头声明，他们尚未说明如何将其转化为行动 ■ 美国的合作预示着今天的美好前景以色列与哈马斯战争之后</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/nasrallahs-long-awaited-speech-could-dictate-the-course-of-the-war-and-lebanons-future/0000018b-9185-db71-a7df-fdcd1cda0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:31:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列为民主而战。现在他正在让它为自己的生命而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</link><description>总理的助手们已经在为内塔尼亚胡战后的政治生存收集弹药，但公众不太可能让他保住自己的席位。他的继任者将不得不面对内塔尼亚胡留下的灾难性遗产</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列尚未从内塔尼亚胡时代的学说中清醒过来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-hasnt-sobered-up-yet-from-its-netanyahu-era-doctrine/0000018b-919e-d477-a1ff-f79ece710000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 00:34:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-hasnt-sobered-up-yet-from-its-netanyahu-era-doctrine/0000018b-919e-d477-a1ff-f79ece710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将税收收入转移给巴勒斯坦权力机构，但扣除流向加沙的资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-palestinian-authority-but-deducts-gaza-bound-funds/0000018b-9255-db7e-af9b-fbd7201a0000</link><description>内阁还决定，以色列将不再允许加沙工人进入该国，并将10月7日在以色列的加沙人送回加沙地带</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 23:47:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-palestinian-authority-but-deducts-gaza-bound-funds/0000018b-9255-db7e-af9b-fbd7201a0000</guid></item><item><title>“耶路撒冷的孩子们问我：圣诞老人，尽管有战争，你还会来吗？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-03/ty-article/.highlight/children-in-jerusalem-ask-me-santa-will-you-come-despite-the-war/0000018b-9247-db71-a7df-ffcfb7f20000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：即使在战争中，以色列唯一经过认证的圣诞老人仍为欢乐而战，度蜜月的新婚夫妇则与家乡的损失作斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 23:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-03/ty-article/.highlight/children-in-jerusalem-ask-me-santa-will-you-come-despite-the-war/0000018b-9247-db71-a7df-ffcfb7f20000</guid></item><item><title>他记录了田园诗般的基布兹的最后几年。他死于哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-captured-his-kibbutzs-final-years-he-died-in-the-hamas-massacre-that-decimated-it/0000018b-9140-db7e-af9b-fbc306ed0000</link><description>就在几个月前，Kfar Azza 的居民动员起来帮助 Yahav Winner 将基布兹变成了他的第一部故事片的拍摄地。拍摄电影和第一个孩子的出生是他一生中最幸福的日子。 10 月 7 日，他在保护家人的过程中被谋杀。他还留下了被毁社区的最后大量文件</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-captured-his-kibbutzs-final-years-he-died-in-the-hamas-massacre-that-decimated-it/0000018b-9140-db7e-af9b-fbc306ed0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对抗内塔尼亚胡的秘密武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bidens-secret-weapon-vis-a-vis-netanyahu/0000018b-91e7-db7e-af9b-fbe75acf0000</link><description>拜登总统没有责骂内塔尼亚胡，而是制定了“紧紧拥抱比比”的策略。最近的书籍揭示了两人在 2021 年加沙一轮战斗中进行的长时间会谈的内容，以及总统断言以色列停止的时候到了</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bidens-secret-weapon-vis-a-vis-netanyahu/0000018b-91e7-db7e-af9b-fbe75acf0000</guid></item><item><title>西岸战争贩子斯莫特里奇必须被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/west-bank-warmonger-smotrich-must-be-fired/0000018b-919e-db71-a7df-fddfcc7e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:32:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/west-bank-warmonger-smotrich-must-be-fired/0000018b-919e-db71-a7df-fddfcc7e0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯抵达以色列推动加沙战斗“人道主义暂停”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-to-push-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-9201-db7e-af9b-fbc392870000</link><description>在前往约旦进行下一站访问之前，预计美国国务卿将向以色列总理内塔尼亚胡和总统赫尔佐格推动他们对战后加沙的愿景</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-to-push-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-9201-db7e-af9b-fbc392870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人在约旦河西岸被杀，定居者焚烧汽车以示报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-west-bank-settlers-torch-cars-in-revenge/0000018b-9116-d477-a1ff-f7162d900000</link><description>巴勒斯坦卫生部报告称，周四，在盖勒吉利耶和比雷赫发生的其他事件中，包括一名 14 岁男孩在内的 3 名巴勒斯坦人被以色列国防军杀害</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 21:39:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-west-bank-settlers-torch-cars-in-revenge/0000018b-9116-d477-a1ff-f7162d900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内政部长不顾财政部长反对向阿拉伯城镇提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-sends-funds-to-arab-towns-over-finance-ministers-objection/0000018b-9117-d7a8-afcf-bbb749840000</link><description>8 月，极右翼宗教犹太复国主义党的财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇 (Bezalel Smotrich) 发誓要暂停提供资金，直到能够证实这笔钱不会落入阿拉伯犯罪分子手中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 19:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-sends-funds-to-arab-towns-over-finance-ministers-objection/0000018b-9117-d7a8-afcf-bbb749840000</guid></item><item><title>内塔亚胡既虚弱又害怕。他必须走</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/nentayahu-is-weak-and-afraid-he-must-go/0000018b-9163-d477-a1ff-f763c5a60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 19:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/nentayahu-is-weak-and-afraid-he-must-go/0000018b-9163-d477-a1ff-f763c5a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席表示，如果医院的燃料耗尽，以色列将允许进入加沙；内塔尼亚胡称他不同意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-israel-to-allow-fuel-into-gaza-for-hospitals-netanyahu-disputes-this/0000018b-9111-d7a8-afcf-bbb377200000</link><description>赫兹尔·哈勒维否认加沙医院燃料短缺的报道，承诺未来进入加沙地带的燃料将受到监控，以免到达哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:44:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-israel-to-allow-fuel-into-gaza-for-hospitals-netanyahu-disputes-this/0000018b-9111-d7a8-afcf-bbb377200000</guid></item><item><title>“系统性的政治迫害”：加沙战争中对以色列-阿拉伯人的迫害是什么样子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/systematic-witch-hunt-what-persecution-of-israeli-arabs-looks-like-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-90db-db7e-af9b-fbdb254e0000</link><description>逮捕、审讯、解雇、大学开除——在最近一波可能撕裂以色列社会脆弱结构的事件中，阿拉伯公民成为以色列安全官员甚至他们自己同事的目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/systematic-witch-hunt-what-persecution-of-israeli-arabs-looks-like-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-90db-db7e-af9b-fbdb254e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列参加意大利漫画节引发加沙战争愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-presence-at-italian-comics-festival-draws-ire-over-gaza-war/0000018b-90e4-d7a8-afcf-bae7b9b60000</link><description>以色列兄弟阿萨夫·哈努卡 (Asaf Hanuka) 和托梅尔·哈努卡 (Tomer Hanuka) 本应在今年的卢卡漫画和游戏节上受到招待，但以色列大使馆的参与导致几位艺术家退出。最终，兄弟俩决定不参加：“我们不想从真正的战争转向媒体战争”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-presence-at-italian-comics-festival-draws-ire-over-gaza-war/0000018b-90e4-d7a8-afcf-bae7b9b60000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的“后天”困境将为真主党的下一步行动铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-day-after-dilemma-will-pave-hezbollahs-next-steps/0000018b-8cce-db71-a7df-fdcf78b80000</link><description>德黑兰正在协助哈马斯、维持其在该地区的其他立足点并避免与美国直接军事对抗</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 17:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-day-after-dilemma-will-pave-hezbollahs-next-steps/0000018b-8cce-db71-a7df-fdcf78b80000</guid></item></channel></rss